{{not|瑞秋}}

'''拉结'''（{{lang-he|'''רחל'''|translit=Rāḥēl|lit=[[Sheep|ewe]]}}）<!--  "Ewe," also "innocence and gentility of a rose" and may mean "lovely". -->，是《[[希伯来圣经|希伯来圣经]]》裡[[以色列|以色列]]族長、[[以色列人|以色列人]][[祖先|祖先]][[雅各_(舊約聖經)|雅各]]的第二位和最宠爱的妻子（兩人是表親），[[古埃及|古埃及]][[維齊爾_(古埃及)|大內總管]][[約瑟_(舊約聖經)|约瑟]]和[[便雅悯|便雅悯]]的母亲，[[拉班|拉班]]的女儿，雅各第一位妻子[[利亚|利亚]]（Leah）的妹妹。丈夫雅各是她的表兄，婆婆[[利百加|利百加]]是拉结的姑母，參見《[[創世記|創世記]]》。

== 生平 ==
=== 出场 ===
拉结在圣经中首次出现，是在{{Bible|创世记|29|17}}，被形容为“生得形貌美丽。”（{{lang-he|'''וְרָחֵל הָֽיְתָה יְפַת־תֹּאַר וִיפַת מַרְאֶה'''}}）。

=== 嫁给雅各 ===
雅各的母亲利百加劝他逃到拉结的家，以免被哥哥[[以扫|以扫]]杀害，也能有机会物色一位妻子。他看见拉结，立刻爱上了她，希望同她结婚，舅舅[[拉班|拉班]]要求雅各为他牧羊7年，但在婚礼的夜晚却哄骗他，将姊姊利亚穿上礼服，冒充拉结嫁给雅各。犹太人中还传说，雅各和拉结怀疑拉班会施行这样的诡计，设计了一连串的暗号，让新郎到时可以识别出蒙头的新娘。可是当拉结發现拉班带利亚前去时，不忍让自己的姊姊在众人面前蒙羞，将暗号透露给了姊姊<ref>Wagensberg, Abba (2006), [http://www.aishdas.org/ta/5767/vayeitzei.pdf "Between The Lines,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aishdas.org/ta/5767/vayeitzei.pdf |date=20200803012257 }} in Toras Aish, Volume XIV, No. 11, © 2006 Rabbi A. Wagensberg & aish.com</ref>。當雅各在結婚[[初夜|初夜]]發現妻子是利亚後，婚姻已經生效。于是雅各接受拉班的要求，再牧羊7年，才有机会娶到了拉结。隨了利亚及拉结外，拉班也給予利亚及拉结的兩個[[侍女|侍女]]給雅各，兩人皆成為雅各的妻子。<ref>Ginzberg, Louis (1909) [http://www.sacred-texts.com/jud/loj/loj108.htm ''The Legends of the Jews''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacred-texts.com/jud/loj/loj108.htm |date=20111105085248 }}, Volume I, Chapter VI: Jacob, at sacred-texts.com</ref> 

=== 母亲 ===
當利亞生了四個兒子後，拉結仍難以懷孕。她讓其[[侍女|侍女]]辟拉給雅各，辟拉再生了兩個兒子，被視為拉結的兒子。利亞再生了兩個兒子及一個女兒，亦使其侍女悉帕生了兩個兒子，拉結自己其後生了兩個兒子。<ref name = "je">[http://jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=57&letter=R&search=rachel '''Rachel'''] {{Wayback|url=http://jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=57&letter=R&search=rachel |date=20100311081812 }} at [http://jewishencyclopedia.com http://jewishencyclopedia.com] {{Wayback|url=http://jewishencyclopedia.com/ |date=20141030080258 }}</ref>'''《[[创世纪|创世纪]]》''' （35章24节）  拉结生—— 约瑟 \ יוֹסֵף                                      [[便雅悯|便雅悯]] \ בִּנְיָמִין

=== 去世与埋葬 ===
据《创世记》记载，拉結生下第二個兒子[[便雅悯|便雅悯]]（Benjamin，原名為便俄尼）後，因[[難產|難產]]而死。雅各在[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]往[[伯利恒|伯利恒]]的路上埋葬拉結，並設立墓碑，今日尚在。

== 后代 ==
拉結所生的長子約瑟成為以色列支派的領袖，他成為[[古埃及|古埃及]]的[[維齊爾_(古埃及)|大內總管]]，期間以色列人移居埃及，在埃及建立自身的民族主義。<ref>[http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=441&letter=J&search=Joseph '''Joseph'''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=441&letter=J&search=Joseph |date=20111011113329 }} at [http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com jewishencyclopedia.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jewishencyclopedia.com/ |date=20011117015119 }}</ref><ref>Davidiy, Yair, [http://www.britam.org/messiah.html "Moshiach Ben Yoseph,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britam.org/messiah.html |date=20210126200852 }} at [http://www.britam.org/ britam.org] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britam.org/ |date=20200808004058 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.truthnet.org/TheMessiah/4_Messiah_of_Judaism/ "The Messiah of Judaism,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.truthnet.org/TheMessiah/4_Messiah_of_Judaism/ |date=20210125032415 }} at [http://www.truthnet.org/ truthnet.org] {{Wayback|url=http://www.truthnet.org/ |date=20201109033932 }}</ref>

<!-- ==Additional references in the Bible==
In [[Book_of_Jeremiah|Jeremiah]] 31:15, the prophet speaks of 'Rachel weeping for her children' ([[KJV|KJV]]). This is interpreted in [[Judaism|Judaism]] as Rachel crying for an end to her descendants' sufferings and exiles following the destruction of the [[First_Temple|First Temple]] in ancient [[Jerusalem|Jerusalem]]. According to the [[Midrash|Midrash]], Rachel spoke before God: "If I, a mere mortal, was not prepared to humiliate my sister and was willing to take a rival into my home, how could You, the eternal, compassionate God, be jealous of [[idolatry|idols]], which have no true existence, that were brought into Your home (the [[Temple_in_Jerusalem|Temple in Jerusalem]])? Will You cause my children to be exiled on this account?" God accepted her plea and promised that, eventually, the exile would end and the Jews would return to their land.<ref>Weisberg, Chana, [http://www.chabad.org/theJewishWoman/article.asp?AID=439609 "Rachel - Biblical Women"] at [http://www.chabad.org chabad.org]</ref>

In the second chapter of the [[Gospel_of_Matthew|Gospel of Matthew]] (part of the [[Christianity|Christian]] [[New_Testament|New Testament]]), this reference from Jeremiah is interpreted as a prediction of the [[Massacre_of_the_Innocents|Massacre of the Innocents]] by [[Herod_the_Great|Herod the Great]] in his attempt to kill the young [[Jesus|Jesus]]. -->

== 其它 ==
在普鲁斯特的代表作，长篇意识流小说《追忆似水年华》中，圣卢侯爵的情妇（她后来成为举世闻名的风格演员）也叫拉结。马塞尔早年去妓院游荡时，也曾听到妓院老板因圣经中的故事戏称她为拉结主托。

